ate=2018-08-24|author=Anoop Gantayat|date=2009-12-08|publisher=Andriasang|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100605081249/http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2009/12/08/chinese_dsi/|archivedate=2010-06-05|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="Anoop2009b">{{cite web|url=http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2009/10/27/nintendo_ds_push/|title=Nintendo Plans DS Push|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=Anoop Gantayat|date=2009-10-27|publisher=Andriasang|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110622234401/http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2009/10/27/nintendo_ds_push/|archivedate=2011-06-22|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

日本任天堂準備了20萬部任天堂DSi作為首發庫存，結果首日即售出超過17萬部{{Notetag|根據[[Enterbrain|Enterbrain]]的估計為170,779部<ref name="Chris2008">{{cite web|url=http://gear.ign.com/articles/927/927390p1.html|title=Japanese Nintendo DSi Sales|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=Chris Iaquinta|date=2008-11-05|work=IGN|publisher=Fox Interactive Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090203002311/http://gear.ign.com/articles/927/927390p1.html|archivedate=2009-02-03|deadurl=no}}</ref>；[[Media_Create|Media Create]]的估計則為171,925部<ref name="Rob2008">{{cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/news/ps3-outsells-all-home-consoles-japan|title=PS3 Outsells All Home Consoles in Japan|author=Rob Crossley|date=2008-11-07|accessdate=2018-08-24|work=Edge|publisher=Future plc|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090205134517/http://www.edge-online.com/news/ps3-outsells-all-home-consoles-japan|archivedate=2009-02-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>。|name=Japanese launch}}，其它3萬部也皆被預訂<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/926/926327p1.html|title=Viewtiful Joe Coming to Tatsunoko VS Capcom|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=John Tanaka|date=2008-11-03|work=IGN|publisher=Fox Interactive Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090103064604/http://wii.ign.com/articles/926/926327p1.html|archivedate=2009-01-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。至2008年11月底，任天堂DSi銷量已達53.5萬部，只略落後於同時期任天堂DS Lite的55萬部<ref name="Ben2008">{{cite web|url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/32542/JAPAN-DSi-sells-half-a-million|title=Japan: DSi sells half a million|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=Ben Parfitt|date=2008-12-02|work=Market for Home Computing and Video Games|publisher=Intent Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090205183425/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/32542/JAPAN-DSi-sells-half-a-million|archivedate=2009-02-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>；在首發兩天內，北美及歐洲的任天堂DSi銷量合計已達60萬部<ref name="Oli2009">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/nintendo-ready-to-revive-the-japanese-market-iwata|title=Nintendo ready to revive the Japanese market – Iwata|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=Oli Welsh|date=2009-04-09|work=GamesIndustry.biz|publisher=Eurogamer Network|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090506034703/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/nintendo-ready-to-revive-the-japanese-market-iwata|archivedate=2009-05-06|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，北美的任天堂DSi首周銷量甚至達同時期任天堂DS Lite銷量的兩倍，來到了43.5萬部<ref name="Tom2009">{{cite web|url=http://www.next-gen.biz/news/dsi-435000-first-week-us-sales|title=DSi: 435,000 First Week US Sales|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=Tom Ivan|date=2009-04-17|work=Edge|publisher=Future plc|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090420173404/http://www.edge-online.com/news/dsi-435000-first-week-us-sales|archivedate=2009-04-20|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。[[File:Nintendo_World_Store_1.png|链接=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Nintendo_World_Store_1.png]]旗艦店。]]任天堂為任天堂DSi舉辦了許多活動，包括在[[紐約|紐約]]的[[紐約任天堂|任天堂世界]]旗艦店及[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]的{{En-link|環球城市大道|Universal CityWalk}}舉辦官方的首發活動<ref name="Ireport" /><ref name="McKinley2009">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/209600/nintendo-dsi-launch-party-universal-studios/|title=Nintendo DSi: Launch Party @ Universal Studios|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=McKinley Noble|date=2009-04-07|work=GamePro|publisher=IDG|pages=1–3|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090611192512/http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/209600/nintendo-dsi-launch-party-universal-studios/|archivedate=2009-06-11|author2=Will Herring|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="Harris2009">{{cite web|url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/968/968133p1.html|title=DSi Launch Party in LA This Saturday|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=Craig Harris|date=2009-03-31|work=IGN|publisher=Fox Interactive Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090403081304/http://ds.ign.com/articles/968/968133p1.html|archivedate=2009-04-03|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.engadget.com/2009/03/30/celebrate-the-dsi-launch-in-los-angeles/|title=Celebrate the DSi launch in Los Angeles|author=|date=|work=|newspaper=Engadget|accessdate=2018-08-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180901044342/https://www.engadget.com/2009/03/30/celebrate-the-dsi-launch-in-los-angeles/|archivedate=2018-09-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>，多達150人徹夜等待[[GameStop|GameStop]]及其他零售通路引進任天堂DSi<ref name="McKinley20092">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/209600/nintendo-dsi-launch-party-universal-studios/|title=Nintendo DSi: Launch Party @ Universal Studios|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=McKinley Noble|date=2009-04-07|work=GamePro|publisher=IDG|pages=1–3|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090611192512/http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/209600/nintendo-dsi-launch-party-universal-studios/|archivedate=2009-06-11|author2=Will Herring|deadurl=no}}</ref>。另外，一部由知名積木藝術家{{En-link|西恩·肯尼|Sean Kenney (artist)}}（Sean Kenney）製作，以[[乐高积木|樂高積木]]組成的大型任天堂DSi模型也同時在紐約任天堂世界展出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnet.com/news/human-size-lego-dsi-model-on-display/|title=Human-sized Lego DSi model|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=John Chan|date=2009-04-08|work=CNET|publisher=CBS Interactive|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140427054946/http://www.cnet.com/news/human-size-lego-dsi-model-on-display/|archivedate=2014-04-27|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

2009年11月21日，任天堂DSi LL於日本發售，首發顏色包括[[古銅色|古銅色]]、[[勃艮第酒紅|酒紅色]]和白色<ref name="fourth2" />；任天堂DSi XL則於2010年3月5日在歐洲、3月28日在北美發售，首發顏色皆包括古銅色及酒紅色<ref name="euro date">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/nintendo-dsi-xl-to-launch-in-europe-in-march|title=Nintendo DSi XL to launch in Europe in March|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=Kath Brice|date=2010-01-14|work=GamesIndustry.biz|publisher=Eurogamer Network|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100117075017/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/nintendo-dsi-xl-to-launch-in-europe-in-march|archivedate=2010-01-17|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="NA summit">{{cite web|url=https://arstechnica.com/gaming/news/2010/02/nintendo-summit-2010.ars|title=Nintendo shows off new DSi, digital games push at summit|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=Michael Thompson|date=2010-02-25|work=Ars Technica|publisher=Condé Nast Publications|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100531135924/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/news/2010/02/nintendo-summit-2010.ars|archivedate=2010-05-31|deadurl=no}}</ref>。在首發兩天內，日本的任天堂DSi LL銷量已達10萬部{{Notetag|根據Enterbrain的估計為103,524部<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.famitsu.com/game/news/1229910_1124.html|publisher=Enterbrain|work=[[Fami通|Fami通]]|title=ニンテンドーDSi LL、発売から2日間で10万3524台を販売(エンターブレイン調べ)|accessdate=2018-08-24|date=2009-11-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121122224000/http://www.famitsu.com/game/news/1229910_1124.html|archivedate=2012-11-22|deadurl=no}}</ref>；Media Create的估計則為100,553部<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/big-in-japan-nov-16-22-dsi-xl-6242052|title=Big in Japan Nov. 16-22: DSi XL|date=2009-12-04|author=Brendan Sinclair|work=GameSpot|publisher=CBS Interactive|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100317112442/http://www.gamespot.com/news/6242052.html|archivedate=2010-03-17|deadurl=no|accessdate=2018-08-31}}</ref>。|name=XL Japanese launch}}；北美方面則在首發三天內，售出了14.1萬部任天堂DSi XL<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34126/Nintendo_3DS_Sells_Just_Under_400000_In_First_Week_Of_US_Sales.php|title=Nintendo 3DS Sells Just Under 400,000 In First Week Of U.S. Sales|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=Kyle Orland|date=2011-04-14|work=Gamasutra|publisher=United Business Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121111082230/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34126/Nintendo_3DS_Sells_Just_Under_400000_In_First_Week_Of_US_Sales.php|archivedate=2012-11-11|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

2010年3月23日，為在該年[[E3電子娛樂展|E3電子娛樂展]]前吸引媒體及消費者的注意，任天堂提前發表了任天堂DS系列的繼任者[[任天堂3DS|任天堂3DS]]<ref name="Ref_2010a">{{cite web|url=https://www.cnbc.com/id/36087758|title=Did Nintendo Doom New Handheld Before Its Release?|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=|date=2010-03-29|work=CNBC|publisher=NBC Universal|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110611042557/http://www.cnbc.com/id/36087758|archivedate=2011-06-11|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="invest QA2">{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/library/events/100507qa/03.html|title=2010年5月7日（金）決算説明会 - 質疑応答|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=岩田聡|date=2010-05-07|publisher=任天堂|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100516020940/http://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/en/library/events/100507qa/03.html|archivedate=2010-05-16|page=3|deadurl=no}}</ref>。此舉大幅影響了任天堂DSi XL在北美的銷量。M2研究的分析師比利·皮吉昂（Billy Pigeon）表示：「在日本，（任天堂）DSi XL（LL）已推出將近一季，日本任天堂總部可能因此而忽略了北美地區的實際情形，而誤判了（任天堂）3DS的公佈時機。」<ref name="Ref_2010a" />許多任天堂股東及投資者因而質疑任天堂高層的決策，時任任天堂社長岩田聰對此則解釋：「那些想要在發表會結束後立即入手任天堂3DS的人，多半對電子遊戲界已非常熟悉；而那些購買任天堂DSi LL（XL）的人則多半不會深入了解現況。」<ref name="invest QA2" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.g4tv.com/thefeed/blog/post/704646/nintendo-doesnt-believe-3ds-announcement-impacted-dsi-xl-sales/|title=Nintendo Doesn't Believe 3DS Announcement Impacted DSi XL Sales|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=Patrick Klepek|date=2010-05-12|publisher=[[G4_(电视频道)|G4]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160921011705/http://www.g4tv.com/thefeed/blog/post/704646/nintendo-doesnt-believe-3ds-announcement-impacted-dsi-xl-sales/|archivedate=2016-09-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
