=== 簡介 ===
任天堂DSi之設計大致與前代主機[[任天堂DS_Lite|任天堂DS Lite]]相同<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/series/dsi/size/index.html|title=ニンテンドーDSi：サイズ|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=|date=|publisher=任天堂|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831212024/https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/series/dsi/size/index.html|archivedate=2018-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/series/dsi/size/compare.html|title=ニンテンドーDSi：ニンテンドーDSiとニンテンドーDS Liteを比較する|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=|date=|publisher=任天堂|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831211854/https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/series/dsi/size/compare.html|archivedate=2018-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。任天堂DSi之主機長度較任天堂DS Lite減少了12%，即{{convert|0.1|in|mm}}，但寬度則較任天堂DS Lite大，重量也較輕<ref name=":0" /><ref name="bitT1">{{cite web|url=http://www.bit-tech.net/gaming/dsi/2009/03/17/nintendo-dsi-review/1|title=Nintendo DSi Review|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=Joe Martin|date=2009-03-17|work=Bit-tech|publisher=Dennis Publishing|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090320033234/http://www.bit-tech.net/gaming/dsi/2009/03/17/nintendo-dsi-review/1|archivedate=2009-03-20|page=1|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="Harris2008a">{{cite web|url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/917/917200p1.html|title=DSi: Just the Facts (And a Little Speculation)|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=Craig Harris|date=2008-10-07|work=IGN|publisher=Fox Interactive Media|pages=1–3|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090317183536/http://ds.ign.com/articles/917/917200p1.html|archivedate=2009-03-17|deadurl=no}}</ref>。任天堂DSi整體風格延續[[任天堂DS系列|任天堂DS系列]]的雙螢幕設計，主機配有兩面對角線寬度為{{convert|3.25|in|mm}}大的[[薄膜電晶體液晶顯示器|薄膜電晶體液晶顯示器]]（TFT-LCD），其較任天堂DS Lite之螢幕尺寸提升了{{convert|0.25|in|mm}}<ref name="bitT1" /><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/series/dsi/index.html|title=ニンテンドーDSi|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=|date=|publisher=任天堂|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005202757/https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/series/dsi/index.html|archivedate=2018-10-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同時發色數為262,144色<ref name=":1" /><ref name="cnet specs">{{cite web|url=http://reviews.cnet.com/consoles/nintendo-dsi-black/4507-10109_7-33319298.html|title=Nintendo DSi specifications|accessdate=2018-08-24|author=|date=|work=CNET|publisher=CBS Interactive|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5q4qjYLyA?url=http://reviews.cnet.com/consoles/nintendo-dsi-black/4507-10109_7-33319298.html|archivedate=2010-05-29|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。主機下方的螢幕具備[[多點觸控|多點觸控]]機能，並支援[[觸控筆|觸控筆]]<ref name=":1" />；內建按鍵包括字母按鍵（A、B、X、Y）、[[十字键|十字鍵]]、左右[[肩鍵|肩鍵]]（L、R）、開始按鈕、選擇按鈕及電源按鈕；主機下方有卡匣插槽、左右肩鍵及電源線孔<ref name=":1" />{{Sfn|Nintendo|2009|pp=8, 11}}。需要注意的是，任天堂DSi附贈的[[交流適配器|交流適配器]]（型號為WAP-002）與其它任天堂DS系列遊戲機皆不相容{{Sfn|Nintendo|2009|p=13}}。

任天堂DSi首度引進了相機功能，配備了兩個30萬[[畫素|畫素]]的[[視訊圖形陣列|影片圖形陣列]]（VGA）相機，分別位於主機螢幕旋轉軸及主機背面<ref name="bitT2">{{cite web|url=http://www.bit-tech.net/gaming/dsi/2009/03/17/nintendo-dsi-review/2|title=Nintendo DSi Review|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Joe Martin|date=2009-03-17|work=Bit-tech|publisher=Dennis Publishing|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090320033239/http://www.bit-tech.net/gaming/dsi/2009/03/17/nintendo-dsi-review/2|archivedate=2009-03-20|page=2|deadurl=no}}</ref>。另外，任天堂DSi首度支援[[SD卡|SD卡]]，插槽位於主機右側<ref name=":1" />。任天堂DSi繼任天堂DS Lite的切換開關之後，再度使用與原版[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]相同的電源按鈕啟動主機，不過按鈕位置與原版任天堂DS不同，改為在主機下方螢幕的左側<ref name="GShands22">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/6201087/p-2.html|title=Nintendo DSi Hands-On|accessdate=2018-08-26|author=Sarju Shah|date=2009-04-03|work=GameSpot|publisher=CBS Interactive|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5q4q30n8d?url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/6201087/p-2.html|archivedate=2010-05-29|page=2|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="Cnet review">{{cite web|url=http://reviews.cnet.com/nintendo-dsi/|title=Nintendo DSi review|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Jeff Bakalar|date=2009-04-05|work=CNET|publisher=CBS Interactive|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090618035743/http://reviews.cnet.com/nintendo-dsi/|archivedate=2009-06-18|deadurl=no}}</ref>。主機左側有亮度及音量控制開關，其中亮度大小有六種選擇，比任天堂DS Lite多了一個；耳機孔則位於主機的下方<ref name="GShands2">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/6201087/p-2.html|title=Nintendo DSi Hands-On|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Sarju Shah|date=2009-04-03|work=GameSpot|publisher=CBS Interactive|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5q4q30n8d?url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/6201087/p-2.html|archivedate=2010-05-29|page=2|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

任天堂DSi採用擁有特殊[[光澤_(光學)|光澤]]的螢幕，以防止沾黏指紋及髒汙<ref name="Iwata Asks p1" />。任天堂DSi有六種不同的主機顏色<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/series/dsi/color/index.html|title=ニンテンドーDSi：カラーバリエーション|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=|date=|publisher=任天堂|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831211926/https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/series/dsi/color/index.html|archivedate=2018-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不過部分特殊顏色曾只於特定地區銷售<ref name="Nintendo2009">{{cite press release|title=Nintendo Unveils Wii Fit Plus Launch Date and New Colors of Nintendo DSi, Wii Remote|publisher=Nintendo of America|date=2009-09-01|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20090831006002/en|accessdate=2018-08-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180901044502/https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20090831006002/en|archivedate=2018-09-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="JP PLgMBcolors">{{cite web|url=http://www.next-gen.biz/news/nintendo-reveals-3-new-dsi-colours|title=Nintendo Reveals 3 New DSi Colours|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Rob Crossley|date=2009-02-25|work=Edge|publisher=Future plc|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101027155932/http://www.next-gen.biz/news/nintendo-reveals-3-new-dsi-colours|archivedate=2010-10-27|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="EU BRMb">{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/2009/new_colours_for_the_nintendo_dsi_14609.html|title=New colours for the Nintendo DSi|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=|date=2009-09-22|publisher=Nintendo of Europe|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5q5ZG9ESo?url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/2009/new_colours_for_the_nintendo_dsi_14609.html|archivedate=2010-05-29|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。例如，{{En-link|萊姆綠色|Lime (color)#Lime (traditional lime green)}}曾為日本限定<ref name="David2009">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/nintendo-unveils-black-coloured-wii-in-japan|title=Nintendo unveils black-coloured Wii in Japan|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=David Jenkins|date=2009-06-04|work=GamesIndustry.biz|publisher=Eurogamer Network|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090607074742/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/nintendo-unveils-black-coloured-wii-in-japan|archivedate=2009-06-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.engadget.com/2009/02/25/three-new-colors-for-dsi-in-japan/|title=Three new colors for DSi in Japan|author=|date=|work=|newspaper=Engadget|accessdate=2018-08-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831211836/https://www.engadget.com/2009/02/25/three-new-colors-for-dsi-in-japan/|archivedate=2018-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而紅色曾只有歐美玩家才可以入手<ref name="EU BRMb" /><ref name="pcmag RB">{{cite web|url=https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2407943,00.asp|title=Nintendo Tips Matte Red, Blue DSi Models|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Angela Moscaritolo|date=2012-08-01|coauthors=Ziff Davis|publisher=PC Magazine|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180901003738/https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2407943,00.asp|archivedate=2018-09-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>；北美版本的藍色任天堂DSi與日版也有些微色調差異<ref name="pcmag RB" />。此外，任天堂還曾發售許多特別塗裝版及同捆版本的任天堂DSi，並曾與《[[逆轉檢事|逆轉檢事]]》及《[[最終幻想水晶編年史_時之回聲|最終幻想水晶編年史 時之回聲]]》等第三方遊戲合作<ref name="John2008">{{cite web|url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/940/940383p1.html|title=Echoes of Time DSi Design Revealed|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=John Tanaka|date=2008-12-22|work=IGN|publisher=Fox Interactive Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090206071808/http://ds.ign.com/articles/940/940383p1.html|archivedate=2009-02-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Justin2009">{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3173566|title=Limited Edition Ace Attorney DSi Coming to Japan|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Justin Haywald|date=2009-04-02|work=1UP.com|publisher=UGO Networks|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120630021441/http://www.1up.com/news/limited-edition-ace-attorney-dsi|archivedate=2012-06-30|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="HaFriday">{{cite web|url=http://techland.time.com/2009/11/23/two-new-nintendo-dsi-bundles-for-black-friday/|title=Two New Nintendo DSi Bundles For Black Friday|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Peter Ha|date=2009-11-23|work=Time|publisher=Time Inc.|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160910051428/http://techland.time.com/2009/11/23/two-new-nintendo-dsi-bundles-for-black-friday/|archivedate=2016-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 任天堂DSi LL ===
任天堂DSi LL為任天堂DSi的大螢幕版本<ref name="spec" /><ref name="fourth2" />。據時任任天堂社長岩田聰在任天堂DSi LL的發表會上表示，「在（任天堂DSi LL）之前，我們因為成本及技術的限制，無法進一步將掌上遊戲機的螢幕擴大，並持續新增功能。如今，任天堂DSi LL不只將螢幕加大，並且還改進了螢幕品質、增大螢幕可視角度，使用戶不必持續以特定角度注視主機螢幕。」<ref name="Briefing">{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/library/events/091030/09.html|title=2009年10月30日（金）経営方針説明会／第2四半期（中間）決算説明会|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=岩田聡|date=2009-10-30|publisher=任天堂|pages=9–10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091106150931/http://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/library/events/091030/09.html|archivedate=2009-11-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>他並表示，相對於注重個人化需求的任天堂DSi，任天堂DSi LL適合「放置於客廳當中」，讓家庭成員共同分享<ref name="Briefing" />。

任天堂DSi LL是任天堂DS全系列遊戲機中體積最大、重量最重的機型<ref name="spec" /><ref name="Anoop2006">{{cite web|url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/687/687783p1.html|title=DS Lite Colors Revealed|accessdate=2018-05-24|author=Anoop Gantayat|date=2006-02-10|work=IGN|publisher=Fox Interactive Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090203170240/http://ds.ign.com/articles/687/687783p1.html|archivedate=2009-02-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，主機配有兩面對角線寬度為{{convert|4.2|in|mm}}大的TFT-LCD顯示器，較任天堂DSi加大了29%，不過螢幕解析度與任天堂DSi相同<ref name="Iwata Asks XL p2" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/dsiLL/size.html|title=ニンテンドーDSi LL：サイズ|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=|date=|publisher=任天堂|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150726155818/http://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/dsiLL/size.html|archivedate=2015-07-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/dsiLL/display.html|title=ニンテンドーDSi LL：画面サイズの比較|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=|publisher=任天堂|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150901045356/http://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/dsiLL/display.html|archivedate=2015-09-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>；任天堂DSi LL還加大了喇叭的大小及音量。任天堂DSi LL預設仰角為120[[度_(角)|°]]，較任天堂DSi的155°小，使玩家在桌面上使用主機時更容易觀看螢幕<ref name="Iwata Asks XL p4">{{cite interview|subject=Masato Kuwahara|subject2=Masaki Amano|subject3=Kazou Yoneyama|subject4=Takaki Fujino|interviewer=Satoru Iwata|title=Nintendo DSi XL|url=http://nintendodsi.com/iwata-asks-chapter.jsp?interviewId=4&volumeId=1&chapterId=4|type=Interview: Transcript|work=Iwata Asks|publisher=任天堂|date=2009-11-30|accessdate=2018-08-25|location=Kyoto, Japan|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110907123938/http://www.nintendodsi.com/iwata-asks-chapter.jsp?interviewId=4&volumeId=1&chapterId=4|archivedate=2011-09-07|deadurl=yes|page=4}}</ref>。任天堂DSi LL附贈了兩支觸控筆<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/dsiLL/touchpen.html|title=ニンテンドーDSi LL：２種類のタッチペン|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=|date=|publisher=任天堂|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150726155828/http://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/dsiLL/touchpen.html|archivedate=2015-07-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中一支可放入主機中，另一隻則較厚、較長<ref name="fourth2" />{{Sfn|Nintendo|2009|p=111}}，需另外放置<ref name="Chris2010">{{cite web|url=https://www.wired.com/reviews/2010/02/pr_dsi_xl|title=Product reviews: Nintendo DSi XL|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Chris Kohler|date=2010-02-01|work=Wired|publisher=Condé Nast Publications|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100812045047/http://www.wired.com/reviews/product/pr_dsi_xl|archivedate=2010-08-12|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

任天堂DSi LL採用了與任天堂DSi相同材質的特殊光澤螢幕，以防止沾黏指紋及髒汙<ref name="ignrev XL">{{cite web|url=http://gear.ign.com/articles/108/1080049p1.html|title=Nintendo DSi XL Review|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Scott Lowe|date=2009-04-06|work=IGN|publisher=Fox Interactive Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100915113759/http://gear.ign.com/articles/108/1080049p1.html|archivedate=2010-09-15|author2=Chris Burke|deadurl=no}}</ref>。任天堂DSi LL有八種不同的主機顏色，不過部分特殊顏色只於特定地區銷售<ref name="Harris2010">{{cite web|url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/109/1095411p1.html|title=Midnight Blue DSi XL in July|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Craig Harris|date=2010-06-08|work=IGN|publisher=Fox Interactive Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110803111223/http://ds.ign.com/articles/109/1095411p1.html|archivedate=2011-08-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="rby AU">{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.com.au/index.php?action=news&nid=309&pageID=6|title=New Colours for Nintendo DSi XL (Plus great new Nintendo DS games)|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=|date=2010-08-26|publisher=Nintendo of Australia|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5sWRqW0Sv?url=http://www.nintendo.com.au/index.php?action=news&nid=309&pageID=6|archivedate=2010-09-05|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="JP byg">{{cite web|url=http://andriasang.com/comlaj/love_plus_plus_special_systems/|title=You'll Love the Love Plus+ DSi LL Systems|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Anoop Gantayat|date=2010-06-02|publisher=Andriasang|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100607043040/http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2010/06/02/love_plus_plus_special_systems/|archivedate=2010-06-07|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，包括白色、綠色<ref name="fourth2" /><ref name="JP byg" /><ref name="EU ygb">{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/2010/a_bright_future_ahead_for_nintendo_dsi_xl_19103.html|title=A bright future ahead for Nintendo DSi XL|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=|date=2010-09-14|publisher=Nintendo of Europe|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5srmvnwfY?url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/2010/a_bright_future_ahead_for_nintendo_dsi_xl_19103.html|archivedate=2010-09-19|deadurl=no}}</ref>、黃色、紅色<ref name="rby AU" /><ref name="EU ygb" />及粉紅色<ref name="pink price">{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/news/dsi-xl-same-price-3ds-pink-color|title=DSi XL, Still the Same Price as a 3DS, Gets Pink as a New Color|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Chris Pereira|date=2011-09-09|work=1UP.com|publisher=UGO Networks|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111015165401/http://www.1up.com/news/dsi-xl-same-price-3ds-pink-color|archivedate=2011-10-15|deadurl=yes}}</ref>等。另外，任天堂還曾發售兩種特別塗裝版本的任天堂DSi LL，分別為《[[LovePlus#迴響與演進|LovePlus+]]》合作版本及《[[超級瑪利歐兄弟|超級瑪利歐兄弟]]》25週年紀念版本<ref name="JP byg" /><ref name="Anoop2010">{{cite web|url=http://andriasang.com/compmc/mario_anniversary_dsi/|title=Nintendo Readying Mario Anniversary DSi LL|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Anoop Gantayat|date=2010-06-02|publisher=Andriasang|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101003231552/http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2010/09/29/mario_anniversary_dsi/|archivedate=2010-10-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

任天堂DSi LL內建了「[[Nintendo_DS_Browser|任天堂DSi瀏覽器]]」及《{{link-en|便攜筆記|Flipnote Studio}}》應用程式，此外根據銷售地區的不同還會附贈其他軟體<ref name="euro date" /><ref name="NA summit" /><ref name="Iwata Asks XL p5">{{cite interview|subject=Masato Kuwahara|subject2=Masaki Amano|subject3=Kazou Yoneyama|subject4=Takaki Fujino|interviewer=Satoru Iwata|title=Nintendo DSi XL|url=http://nintendodsi.com/iwata-asks-chapter.jsp?interviewId=4&volumeId=1&chapterId=5|type=Interview: Transcript|work=Iwata Asks|publisher=任天堂|date=2009-11-30|accessdate=2018-08-25|location=Kyoto, Japan|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110904172447/http://www.nintendodsi.com/iwata-asks-chapter.jsp?interviewId=4&volumeId=1&chapterId=5|archivedate=2011-09-04|deadurl=yes|page=5}}</ref><ref name="Chris2009a">{{cite web|url=http://www.totalvideogames.com/Nintendo-DS/news/Nintendo-Announces-DSi-LL-14707.html|title=Nintendo Announces DSi LL News|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Chris Leyton|date=2009-10-29|work=Total Video Games|publisher=TVG Media Ltd|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091101104532/http://www.totalvideogames.com/Nintendo-DS/news/Nintendo-Announces-DSi-LL-14707.html|archivedate=2009-11-01|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

=== 技術規格 ===
[[File:Nintendo_DSi_main_and_sub_pcb.jpg|链接=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Nintendo_DSi_main_and_sub_pcb.jpg]]。]]任天堂DSi較任天堂DS Lite擁有更快的[[中央處理器|中央處理器]]（CPU）及更多的[[隨機存取記憶體|隨機存取記憶體]]（RAM）<ref name="cnet">{{cite web|url=http://news.cnet.com/gaming-preview-who-should-buy-the-nintendo-dsi-and-who-shouldnt/|title=Gaming preview: Who should buy the Nintendo DSi and who shouldn't|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Jeff Bakalar|date=2009-02-20|work=CNET|publisher=CBS Interactive|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110617083914/http://news.cnet.com/gaming-preview-who-should-buy-the-nintendo-dsi-and-who-shouldnt/|archivedate=2011-06-17|deadurl=no}}</ref>；根據運行遊戲的不同，主機還可以自動分配及運用運算資源，達到效能最大化<ref name="Harris2009a">{{cite web|url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/951/951086p2.html|title=Virtual Console on DSi?|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Craig Harris|date=2009-02-04|work=IGN|publisher=Fox Interactive Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090226095909/http://ds.ign.com/articles/951/951086p2.html|archivedate=2009-02-26|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="hackmii">{{cite web|url=http://hackmii.com/2009/01/dsibrew/|title=DSibrew?|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Bushing|date=2009-01-25|publisher=HackMii|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180901044429/https://hackmii.com/2009/01/dsibrew/|archivedate=2018-09-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。任天堂DSi透過專用的[[編解碼器|編程]][[積體電路|積體電路]]（即[[微處理器|微處理器]]）放大音效音量、提升音效品質，並將音效由[[數位訊號|數位訊號]]轉為[[類比訊號|類比訊號]]輸出。任天堂也將任天堂DSi[[主機板|主機板]]上多餘的空間減去、重新調整中央處理器位置，並加大電池容量<ref name="Iwata Asks p2" />。

任天堂DSi首度引進了相機功能，其相機解析度為30萬[[畫素|畫素]]，較多數行動電話及數位相機都低。據任天堂表示，由於多數軟體皆會使用相機，此舉可大幅加快相機[[反應時間|反應速度]]，同時節省組建成本<ref name="Iwata Asks p1" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/news/gdc-2009-inspired-dsi|title=GDC 2009: What Inspired the DSi's Creation?|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Ray Barnholt|date=2009-03-26|work=1UP.com|publisher=UGO Networks|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019143137/http://www.1up.com/news/gdc-2009-inspired-dsi|archivedate=2012-10-19|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

* 中央處理器（CPU）：任天堂DSi/DSi LL有兩個[[安謀控股|安謀]][[ARM架構|ARM架構]]的處理器，分別為頻率134[[MHz|MHz]]的{{En-link|ARM9|}}及頻率33MHz的[[ARM7|ARM7]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2010/09/23/the-nintendo-3ds-vs-the-world|title=The Nintendo 3DS vs. The World|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Scott Lowe|date=2010-09-22|work=IGN|publisher=Fox Interactive Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120120104213/http://www.ign.com/articles/2010/09/23/the-nintendo-3ds-vs-the-world|archivedate=2012-01-20|deadurl=no}}</ref>，其ARM9處理器速度是前代主機任天堂DS Lite的兩倍<ref name="cnet" /><ref name="pcworld nz">{{cite journal|title=Nintendo DSi: Handheld console|author=Jan Birkeland|url=http://pcworld.co.nz/pcworld/pcw.nsf/reviews/C38AEE5112690F4ECC2575C1000A4FBE|date=2009-05-26|journal=PC World|publisher=Fairfax Media Business Group|accessdate=2018-08-31|issue=|doi=|others=|year=|volume=|page=|pmid=|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5q4p9MiDi?url=http://pcworld.co.nz/pcworld/pcw.nsf/reviews/C38AEE5112690F4ECC2575C1000A4FBE|archivedate=2010-05-29|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。
* 隨機存取記憶體（RAM）：16[[百萬位元組|MB]]，是前代主機的四倍<ref name="bitT1" />。
* 螢幕解析度：256 × 192，與前代主機相同<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/549/549922p1.html|title=Nintendo DS Specs|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Craig Harris|date=2004-09-20|work=IGN|publisher=Fox Interactive Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100706181331/http://ds.ign.com/articles/549/549922p1.html|archivedate=2010-07-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* 相機解析度：30萬[[畫素|畫素]]（640 × 480，即[[480p|480p]]）。
* 儲存空間：內建[[快閃記憶體|快閃記憶體]]，容量為256MB<ref name="dsiVs">{{cite web|url=http://uk.ds.ign.com/articles/926/926277p1.html|title=DSi Versus The Internet|accessdate=2018-08-25|author=Anoop Gantayat|date=2008-11-01|work=IGN|publisher=Fox Interactive Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090122125657/http://uk.ds.ign.com/articles/926/926277p1.html|archivedate=2009-01-22|deadurl=no}}</ref>，並附有[[擴充卡|擴充插槽]]，支援[[SD卡|SD卡]]（最多擴充2[[吉位元組|GB]]）及[[SDHC卡|SDHC卡]]（最多擴充32GB）<ref name="SD FAQ">{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.com/consumer/systems/dsi/en_na/sdCards.jsp|title=Nintendo DSi & Nintendo DSi XL – SD Cards|accessdate=2018-08-26|author=|date=|work=Nintendo of America|publisher=Nintendo|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5s84TY1DJ?url=http://www.nintendo.com/consumer/systems/dsi/en_na/sdCards.jsp|archivedate=2010-08-20|deadurl=no}}</ref>。
* 電池：容量為840[[毫安培小時|毫安培]]，較前代主機任天堂DS Lite的1000毫安培少<ref name="GShands22" />；循環充電次數約為500次{{Sfn|Nintendo|2009|p=13}}。在最低亮度設定的情形下，任天堂DSi電池續航力最多可達9至14小時，任天堂DSi LL電池續航力最多可達13至17小時，不過皆較任天堂DS Lite的15至19小時短<ref name="Harris2008a" /><ref name="GShands22" />。

== 系統功能 ==
{{Main|任天堂DSi系統軟體}}
[[File:Dsi_closed_traced.svg|链接=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Dsi_closed_traced.svg]]任天堂DSi採用的[[作業系統|作業系統]]為任天堂DSi系統軟體，與任天堂的家用遊戲機[[Wii|Wii]]相同，也可透過網路升級[[韌體|韌體]]<ref name="Ireport" /><ref name="businessRev">{{cite journal|title=Nintendo's New DSi: Well Worth the Money|author=Cliff Edwards|url=http://www.businessweek.com/technology/content/apr2009/tc2009049_147316.htm|date=2009-04-10|journal=BusinessWeek|publisher=McGraw-Hill|accessdate=2018-08-26|issue=|doi=|others=|year=|volume=|page=|pmid=|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5q5b0luez?url=http://www.businessweek.com/technology/content/apr2009/tc2009049_147316.htm|archivedate=2010-05-29|deadurl=no}}</ref>。任天堂DSi系統軟體將遊戲及應用程式以圖示方式呈現<ref name="Ireport" />，預設內建有七個圖示，分別為「卡匣內遊戲」、「任天堂DSi照相館」、「任天堂DSi音樂館」、「任天堂DSi商店」、「[[任天堂DS#無線通訊|任天堂DS下載遊玩]]」、「{{En-link|PictoChat|}}」及「系統設定」，其他應用程式則可以在任天堂DSi商店中取得；玩家可以使用手指或觸控筆，自由調整圖示的位置{{Sfn|Nintendo|2009|pp=24–25}}。依據按壓電源按鈕的時間長度及地點，可以[[重新啟動|重置]]主機、返回主畫面或關閉主機。另外，任天堂DSi支援[[熱插拔|熱插拔]]機能，玩家可以在不重啟主機的情況下直接替換遊戲卡匣<ref name="Iwata Asks p4">{{cite interview|subject=Masato Kuwahara|subject2=Yui Ehara|subject3=Kentaro Mita|interviewer=Satoru Iwata|title=Nintendo DSi (Volume 1 – Hardware)|url=http://www.nintendodsi.com/iwata-asks-chapter.jsp?interviewId=1&volumeId=1&chapterId=4|type=Interview: Transcript|work=Iwata Asks|publisher=任天堂|accessdate=2018-08-26|location=Kyoto, Japan|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110809201956/http://www.nintendodsi.com/iwata-asks-chapter.jsp?interviewId=1&volumeId=1&chapterId=4|archivedate=2011-08-09|deadurl=yes|page=4}}</ref>。

任天堂DSi比任天堂DS系列的其它主機支援更多[[多媒體|多媒體]]格式。透過外接SD卡，可以讓主機存取[[進階音訊編碼|進階音訊編碼]]（AAC）音訊檔案、圖片、影片及其它應用程式<ref name="Sarju2009">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/6201087/index.html|title=Nintendo DSi Hands-On|accessdate=2018-08-26|author=Sarju Shah|date=2009-04-03|work=GameSpot|publisher=CBS Interactive|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5q4sKhYVn?url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/6201087/index.html|archivedate=2010-05-29|page=1|deadurl=no}}</ref>，其中圖片及應用程式還可轉移至內建儲存空間<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/213467/features/7-dsi-features-you-may-have-missed/|title=7 DSi Features You May Have Missed|accessdate=2018-08-26|author=Mike Jackson|date=2009-04-24|work=ComputerAndVideoGames.com|publisher=Future plc|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090427130348/http://computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=213467|archivedate=2009-04-27|deadurl=no}}</ref>。「任天堂DSi照相館」應用程式中附有十種[[滤镜|濾鏡]]特效，在攝影前可選擇效果套用<ref name="IGN handson">{{cite web|url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/927/927128p2.html|title=IGN: Nintendo DSi Hands-on|accessdate=2018-08-26|author=Craig Harris|date=2008-11-05|work=IGN|publisher=Fox Interactive Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090223035532/http://ds.ign.com/articles/927/927128p2.html|archivedate=2009-02-23|page=2|deadurl=no}}</ref>{{Sfn|Nintendo|2009|pp=29–31}}。相片可以上傳至Wii的「[[Wii頻道#相片頻道|相片頻道]]」中，並透過電視觀賞；在系統版本1.4升級後，還加入了對社群網站[[Facebook|Facebook]]的支援<ref name="nintendo_a">{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.com/consumer/systems/dsi/en_na/facebook.jsp|title=Facebook integration with the Nintendo DSi Camera|accessdate=2018-08-26|author=|date=|publisher=Nintendo of America|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5q5cOOiYa?url=http://www.nintendo.com/consumer/systems/dsi/en_na/facebook.jsp|archivedate=2010-05-29|deadurl=no}}</ref>{{Sfn|Satoru Iwata|2008|p=3}}。

「任天堂DSi音樂館」應用程式擁有播放音樂及錄音功能。錄製完畢後的音效檔案可以在應用程式內進行音高調整及[[電子濾波器|濾波器]]套用等操作，最多可以儲存18個長度為10秒的音效檔<ref name="GShands22" />。不過，音效檔無法轉移至SD卡上<ref name="SD FAQ" />。另外，玩家還可以透過外接SD卡播放音樂<ref name="GShands22" />，支援的格式包括採用[[.mp4|.mp4]]、[[Apple_Lossless|.m4a]]、[[3GP|.3gp]]等副檔名的音訊檔案，非AAC編碼的檔案格式如[[.mp3|.mp3]]等則無法播放{{Sfn|Nintendo|2009|p=102}}；在播放音樂時，也可同時套用濾波器特效<ref name="GShands22" />。透過耳機，還可以在合上主機後繼續聆聽音樂<ref name="NA DSi date" />。

在任天堂DS系列的繼任者[[任天堂3DS|任天堂3DS]]發售後，任天堂為任天堂DSi推出了專用的轉移軟體，可以將任天堂DSi主機上的圖片、音訊檔案及網路設定轉移至任天堂3DS<ref name="ware licenses">{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.com/consumer/systems/3ds/en_na/gi_index.jsp?menu=transfer&submenu=ctr-gi-apps-transfer-what-data|title=What Is Transferred During the Data Transfer Process?|accessdate=2018-08-27|author=|date=|publisher=Nintendo of America|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130627102154/http://www.nintendo.com/consumer/systems/3ds/en_na/gi_index.jsp?menu=transfer&submenu=ctr-gi-apps-transfer-what-data|archivedate=2013-06-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
